{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-js","path":"/blog/74bd","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"74bd"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Font development and Wayfinding System for Art Research Center","author":"Minkyoung Lee, Lab of Prof. Kymn Kyungsun","date":"March 15th, 2015","hero_image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.8203883495145632,"src":"/static/5bd5883252732cff079798b9ff9e88b7/d6e14/74bd-0.jpg","srcSet":"/static/5bd5883252732cff079798b9ff9e88b7/8def4/74bd-0.jpg 375w,\n/static/5bd5883252732cff079798b9ff9e88b7/35c3d/74bd-0.jpg 750w,\n/static/5bd5883252732cff079798b9ff9e88b7/d6e14/74bd-0.jpg 1129w","sizes":"(max-width: 1129px) 100vw, 1129px"}}}},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Client | Seoul National University </li>\n<li>Cowork | Minkyoung Lee (senior researcher), Prof. Kymn Kyungsun (director), Sohee Kim (researcher), Hye-eun Lim (researcher), Doyeon Yang (researcher)</li>\n<li>Duration | 3 months</li>\n<li>Responsibility | project management, font development, logo production, sign system design and production, supervise graphic design, user scenario and examination</li>\n<li>Tools | Indesign, Illustrator, Photoshop, SketchUp</li>\n<li>Awards | SEGD Merit Award 2017, It Award 2015</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd 2\"\n        title=\"74bd 2\"\n        src=\"/static/dd8957b765867bd0d4374ce7cd23e740/a2510/74bd-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dd8957b765867bd0d4374ce7cd23e740/0479a/74bd-2.jpg 250w,\n/static/dd8957b765867bd0d4374ce7cd23e740/41099/74bd-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/dd8957b765867bd0d4374ce7cd23e740/a2510/74bd-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/dd8957b765867bd0d4374ce7cd23e740/c58a3/74bd-2.jpg 1500w,\n/static/dd8957b765867bd0d4374ce7cd23e740/3acf0/74bd-2.jpg 2000w,\n/static/dd8957b765867bd0d4374ce7cd23e740/856de/74bd-2.jpg 3584w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>This project won awards in <a style=\"color: blue\" href=\"https://segd.org/seoul-national-university-arts-research-center-wayfinding\" target=\"_blank\">2017 SEGD Global Design Award</a> and <a style=\"color: blue\" href=\"https://itaward.or.kr/jsp/award/awardView.jsp?id=60\" target=\"_blank\">IT Award 2015</a>. </p>\n<p>The Seoul National University Arts Research Center is a shared-use facility for the College of Fine Arts and the College of Music. Due to the unique structural form, which resembles a convergence of masses, the flow of movement through the space intersects across various levels and in varying directions. Our goal was to develop a unique wayfinding strategy and its identity system that makes navigating this complex space comfortable. We also expect that the graphic design and exclusive font applied to the sign system will provide users with an unique experience in this space.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 999px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd motif 1\"\n        title=\"74bd motif 1\"\n        src=\"/static/dbc3fa2b91074f154faaca0f2d5d197d/53d2d/74bd-motif-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dbc3fa2b91074f154faaca0f2d5d197d/0479a/74bd-motif-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/dbc3fa2b91074f154faaca0f2d5d197d/41099/74bd-motif-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/dbc3fa2b91074f154faaca0f2d5d197d/53d2d/74bd-motif-1.jpg 999w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 999px) 100vw, 999px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 35.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd motif 2\"\n        title=\"74bd motif 2\"\n        src=\"/static/14cdced97ba41dbf65aa1d686c0d16ae/a2510/74bd-motif-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/14cdced97ba41dbf65aa1d686c0d16ae/0479a/74bd-motif-2.jpg 250w,\n/static/14cdced97ba41dbf65aa1d686c0d16ae/41099/74bd-motif-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/14cdced97ba41dbf65aa1d686c0d16ae/a2510/74bd-motif-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/14cdced97ba41dbf65aa1d686c0d16ae/c58a3/74bd-motif-2.jpg 1500w,\n/static/14cdced97ba41dbf65aa1d686c0d16ae/3acf0/74bd-motif-2.jpg 2000w,\n/static/14cdced97ba41dbf65aa1d686c0d16ae/3a9e8/74bd-motif-2.jpg 2480w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><b> CHALLENGE </b></p>\n<p>The distinct structure built on the slope of a hill without a designated ‘ground-floor’ level as there are entrances and exits on each floor where the building meets the hillside. Students, faculty and visitors enter the building in relation to which part of the campus they are approaching the building from, so there is no clearly defined area to welcome and direct them to their destination, which leads to confusion.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd motif 3\"\n        title=\"74bd motif 3\"\n        src=\"/static/b51b55900aa46e62c265e848aec7bf2d/a2510/74bd-motif-3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b51b55900aa46e62c265e848aec7bf2d/0479a/74bd-motif-3.jpg 250w,\n/static/b51b55900aa46e62c265e848aec7bf2d/41099/74bd-motif-3.jpg 500w,\n/static/b51b55900aa46e62c265e848aec7bf2d/a2510/74bd-motif-3.jpg 1000w,\n/static/b51b55900aa46e62c265e848aec7bf2d/961c1/74bd-motif-3.jpg 1190w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd motif 4\"\n        title=\"74bd motif 4\"\n        src=\"/static/d7d60ba39d1dfc7be61d3a113c61f586/a2510/74bd-motif-4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d7d60ba39d1dfc7be61d3a113c61f586/0479a/74bd-motif-4.jpg 250w,\n/static/d7d60ba39d1dfc7be61d3a113c61f586/41099/74bd-motif-4.jpg 500w,\n/static/d7d60ba39d1dfc7be61d3a113c61f586/a2510/74bd-motif-4.jpg 1000w,\n/static/d7d60ba39d1dfc7be61d3a113c61f586/c58a3/74bd-motif-4.jpg 1500w,\n/static/d7d60ba39d1dfc7be61d3a113c61f586/b17f8/74bd-motif-4.jpg 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>We developed a special font to express its characteristics getting an idea from the building's rough finishing materials. To maintain the building's atmosphere and for a quick implement of our work, we decided to develop a font that is similar to a stencil font. We invented it with two different styles of edges, round and sharp ones, to represent the meaning of art complex having two-sided properties of research and art. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.39999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd design 2\"\n        title=\"74bd design 2\"\n        src=\"/static/e5335e53783d49099e1e6e23778a0307/a2510/74bd-design-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e5335e53783d49099e1e6e23778a0307/0479a/74bd-design-2.jpg 250w,\n/static/e5335e53783d49099e1e6e23778a0307/41099/74bd-design-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/e5335e53783d49099e1e6e23778a0307/a2510/74bd-design-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/e5335e53783d49099e1e6e23778a0307/c58a3/74bd-design-2.jpg 1500w,\n/static/e5335e53783d49099e1e6e23778a0307/3acf0/74bd-design-2.jpg 2000w,\n/static/e5335e53783d49099e1e6e23778a0307/13df2/74bd-design-2.jpg 3100w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd font 1\"\n        title=\"74bd font 1\"\n        src=\"/static/7e2a43e78b27e3af56057f6331a14dbe/a2510/74bd-font-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7e2a43e78b27e3af56057f6331a14dbe/0479a/74bd-font-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/7e2a43e78b27e3af56057f6331a14dbe/41099/74bd-font-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/7e2a43e78b27e3af56057f6331a14dbe/a2510/74bd-font-1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/7e2a43e78b27e3af56057f6331a14dbe/c58a3/74bd-font-1.jpg 1500w,\n/static/7e2a43e78b27e3af56057f6331a14dbe/ca222/74bd-font-1.jpg 1984w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.400000000000006%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd font 2\"\n        title=\"74bd font 2\"\n        src=\"/static/58b0957079ae795cd78eeaadc3719df6/a2510/74bd-font-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/58b0957079ae795cd78eeaadc3719df6/0479a/74bd-font-2.jpg 250w,\n/static/58b0957079ae795cd78eeaadc3719df6/41099/74bd-font-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/58b0957079ae795cd78eeaadc3719df6/a2510/74bd-font-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/58b0957079ae795cd78eeaadc3719df6/d165a/74bd-font-2.jpg 1400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd font 3\"\n        title=\"74bd font 3\"\n        src=\"/static/d180a773070f1447972f8d92a00f1aed/a2510/74bd-font-3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d180a773070f1447972f8d92a00f1aed/0479a/74bd-font-3.jpg 250w,\n/static/d180a773070f1447972f8d92a00f1aed/41099/74bd-font-3.jpg 500w,\n/static/d180a773070f1447972f8d92a00f1aed/a2510/74bd-font-3.jpg 1000w,\n/static/d180a773070f1447972f8d92a00f1aed/c58a3/74bd-font-3.jpg 1500w,\n/static/d180a773070f1447972f8d92a00f1aed/3acf0/74bd-font-3.jpg 2000w,\n/static/d180a773070f1447972f8d92a00f1aed/6a2cd/74bd-font-3.jpg 5700w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>It was planned to be developed only in Korean and limited numbers of symbols, but we also produced English version in consideration of the integrity of the sign system design and thinking that it may be needed in the future.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 113.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd research 3\"\n        title=\"74bd research 3\"\n        src=\"/static/5de10b6daa30d9354911630560ac5e6c/a2510/74bd-research-3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5de10b6daa30d9354911630560ac5e6c/0479a/74bd-research-3.jpg 250w,\n/static/5de10b6daa30d9354911630560ac5e6c/41099/74bd-research-3.jpg 500w,\n/static/5de10b6daa30d9354911630560ac5e6c/a2510/74bd-research-3.jpg 1000w,\n/static/5de10b6daa30d9354911630560ac5e6c/c58a3/74bd-research-3.jpg 1500w,\n/static/5de10b6daa30d9354911630560ac5e6c/3acf0/74bd-research-3.jpg 2000w,\n/static/5de10b6daa30d9354911630560ac5e6c/9c9b2/74bd-research-3.jpg 2268w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>To implement the installation of signages, we made a user scenario. We counted the first floor as the main entrance because it has the largest door of the building and is accessible to other facilities. Therefore, we drew user flows into consideration of the accessibility of users as well as the frequency of use of internal facilities such as classrooms, workrooms, and public spaces.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 113.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd research 4\"\n        title=\"74bd research 4\"\n        src=\"/static/30e306b6166ca39f67ba189e831f008e/a2510/74bd-research-4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/30e306b6166ca39f67ba189e831f008e/0479a/74bd-research-4.jpg 250w,\n/static/30e306b6166ca39f67ba189e831f008e/41099/74bd-research-4.jpg 500w,\n/static/30e306b6166ca39f67ba189e831f008e/a2510/74bd-research-4.jpg 1000w,\n/static/30e306b6166ca39f67ba189e831f008e/c58a3/74bd-research-4.jpg 1500w,\n/static/30e306b6166ca39f67ba189e831f008e/3acf0/74bd-research-4.jpg 2000w,\n/static/30e306b6166ca39f67ba189e831f008e/9c9b2/74bd-research-4.jpg 2268w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>To examine the developed user-scenarios, we conduct analyses of the facility with its accessible points, foot traffic heat-maps, and the facility’s location in relation to the campus. Surprisingly known by the heat-maps, it was found that most students did not enter on the ‘first’ floor of the structure, and would rarely enter and exit the structure through the same door or even the same floor. Therefore, we made additional signboards in addition to the one we were going to install. One of them is a floor guide. This was able to effectively create an effect of image itself, not like normal installation. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 113.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd research 5\"\n        title=\"74bd research 5\"\n        src=\"/static/3e51d02c04a42ba12e78346ef080ce63/a2510/74bd-research-5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3e51d02c04a42ba12e78346ef080ce63/0479a/74bd-research-5.jpg 250w,\n/static/3e51d02c04a42ba12e78346ef080ce63/41099/74bd-research-5.jpg 500w,\n/static/3e51d02c04a42ba12e78346ef080ce63/a2510/74bd-research-5.jpg 1000w,\n/static/3e51d02c04a42ba12e78346ef080ce63/c58a3/74bd-research-5.jpg 1500w,\n/static/3e51d02c04a42ba12e78346ef080ce63/3acf0/74bd-research-5.jpg 2000w,\n/static/3e51d02c04a42ba12e78346ef080ce63/9c9b2/74bd-research-5.jpg 2268w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 933px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 102.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd research 5 1\"\n        title=\"74bd research 5 1\"\n        src=\"/static/8af89467e6c025908c460cf695e69dfb/ac746/74bd-research-5-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8af89467e6c025908c460cf695e69dfb/0479a/74bd-research-5-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/8af89467e6c025908c460cf695e69dfb/41099/74bd-research-5-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/8af89467e6c025908c460cf695e69dfb/ac746/74bd-research-5-1.jpg 933w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 933px) 100vw, 933px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>We have established the installation location of the sign through written user scenarios and validation. The same installation was fine-tuned because the entrances, structures, and use patterns differed from floor to floor.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 113.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd research 6\"\n        title=\"74bd research 6\"\n        src=\"/static/90789c0b18e22f1abcec610dc61a238e/a2510/74bd-research-6.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/90789c0b18e22f1abcec610dc61a238e/0479a/74bd-research-6.jpg 250w,\n/static/90789c0b18e22f1abcec610dc61a238e/41099/74bd-research-6.jpg 500w,\n/static/90789c0b18e22f1abcec610dc61a238e/a2510/74bd-research-6.jpg 1000w,\n/static/90789c0b18e22f1abcec610dc61a238e/c58a3/74bd-research-6.jpg 1500w,\n/static/90789c0b18e22f1abcec610dc61a238e/3acf0/74bd-research-6.jpg 2000w,\n/static/90789c0b18e22f1abcec610dc61a238e/9c9b2/74bd-research-6.jpg 2268w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 882px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 107.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd research 6 1\"\n        title=\"74bd research 6 1\"\n        src=\"/static/3ab056ac304dfe818554339aceb27be6/51568/74bd-research-6-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3ab056ac304dfe818554339aceb27be6/0479a/74bd-research-6-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/3ab056ac304dfe818554339aceb27be6/41099/74bd-research-6-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/3ab056ac304dfe818554339aceb27be6/51568/74bd-research-6-1.jpg 882w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 882px) 100vw, 882px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>We solved the problem of people being confused about which floor they were standing on. We placed wayfinding graphics on the floor at the top of each staircase.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 89.60000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd appy 1\"\n        title=\"74bd appy 1\"\n        src=\"/static/57771639b737e8b106195a368a245ac8/a2510/74bd-appy-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/57771639b737e8b106195a368a245ac8/0479a/74bd-appy-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/57771639b737e8b106195a368a245ac8/41099/74bd-appy-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/57771639b737e8b106195a368a245ac8/a2510/74bd-appy-1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/57771639b737e8b106195a368a245ac8/c58a3/74bd-appy-1.jpg 1500w,\n/static/57771639b737e8b106195a368a245ac8/4e286/74bd-appy-1.jpg 1582w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd appy 3\"\n        title=\"74bd appy 3\"\n        src=\"/static/fd23c36bf380684310f14046501cc8d9/a2510/74bd-appy-3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fd23c36bf380684310f14046501cc8d9/0479a/74bd-appy-3.jpg 250w,\n/static/fd23c36bf380684310f14046501cc8d9/41099/74bd-appy-3.jpg 500w,\n/static/fd23c36bf380684310f14046501cc8d9/a2510/74bd-appy-3.jpg 1000w,\n/static/fd23c36bf380684310f14046501cc8d9/c58a3/74bd-appy-3.jpg 1500w,\n/static/fd23c36bf380684310f14046501cc8d9/76188/74bd-appy-3.jpg 1772w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>All graphics were designed and placed in consideration of natural viewing angles and distances for users. We considered every point of approaching to maximize the presence of wayfinding signage. We also cared about minimizing environmental impact on the look and feel of the space.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"74bd appy 4\"\n        title=\"74bd appy 4\"\n        src=\"/static/18083fcf16230e1a9fd000a4eb65a8fd/a2510/